
List of examples of positive wordplay-like alteringof sayings in lyrics of songs (not as lines of lyrics but as abstract meaning). The first word of the altering is always the same:
- "make hay while the sun shines" -> "make hay while the sun sets"
- "laughter is the best medicine" -> "laughter is the best therapy"
