- "beauty is in the eye of the beholder" -> "beauty is in the eye of the photoshop artist"
- "there's no such thing as a free lunch" -> "there's always a catch to a free lunch"
- "the grass is always greener on the other side" -> "the grass is always greener where you can't see it"
- "a picture is worth a thousand words" -> "a picture can be worth a thousand lies"
- "curiosity killed the cat" -> "curiosity killed the cat and gave it nine lives"
